<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to NeighborTools!</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; }
    .header { background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>NeighborTools</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, {{firstName}}!</h2>
      <p>Thank you for joining NeighborTools - the tool sharing platform for your neighborhood.</p>
      <p>With NeighborTools, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Share your tools with neighbors</li>
        <li>Borrow tools from your community</li>
        <li>Join or create neighborhoods</li>
        <li>Manage your lending history</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Get started by joining a neighborhood or adding your first tool!</p>
      <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="button">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; NeighborTools. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
